@node Usage "How to use the extrq maps"
@{b}Usage:@{ub}

    When generating the screens of your worm stage, press the right button, and give one of the following names in

	* Unforgiven
	* Strange
	* Egypt
	* Platforms

    and it will load the right file, happy worming

